text: Henry Sewell (7 September 1807 – 14 May 1879) was a New Zealand politician. He is the first Premier of New Zealand. He later became Colonial Treasurer (1856–59), as Attorney-General (1861–62), and twice as Minister of Justice (1864–65, 1869–72). ==References== * * * * * Category:1807 births Category:1879 deaths Category:Prime Ministers of New Zealand Category:English lawyers
title: Henry Sewell
